"vostre Tails trencat al vostre nou Tails:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   Try the technique using the [[*Disks* utility|fsck#disks]] first, then the\n"
"   technique using [[`ddrescue`|fsck#ddrescue]] if needed.\n"
